# Absolute API base URL — required for the Capacitor Android build (its
# WebView has no dev-proxy, unlike `npm run dev` in a browser). Leave unset
# for browser dev/production-same-origin deploys; set before building the
# APK, e.g.:
#   Local testing on your own WiFi: http://<your-machine-LAN-IP>:4000
#   Real deployment: https://your-deployed-server.example.com
VITE_API_URL=
